Analyze Image Content With Vision (Legac.code:
// Ask a question about an image (URL or base64 data URI).
// Override `messages` to attach an image part alongside the text.
prompt(null, {
  model: 'gpt-4o-mini',
  messages: [
    {
      role: 'user',
      content: [
        { type: 'text', text: 'Describe what is happening in this image.' },
        { type: 'image_url', image_url: { url: $.data.imageUrl } },
      ],
    },
  ],
});

Conversation (Legacy).code:
// Multi-turn chat. Provide the full message history via `messages`.
// `prompt`'s first arg is ignored here because we override `messages`.
prompt(null, {
  model: 'gpt-4o-mini',
  messages: [
    { role: 'system', content: 'You are a concise assistant.' },
    ...($.state.history || []),
    { role: 'user', content: $.data.userMessage },
  ],
  temperature: 0.5,
});

